agdm&t=s Maps of Chicago from the American Geographical Society Library]\n* {{HALS |survey=IL-10 |id=il0993 |title=Chicago Cityscape, Chicago, Cook County, IL |photos=45 |cap=4}}\n* [https://localwiki.org/chicago// Chicago \u2013 LocalWiki] Local Chicago Wiki\n\n{{Chicago}}\n{{Navboxes\n|list =\n{{Community areas of Chicago}}\n{{Neighborhoods in Chicago}}\n{{Cook County, Illinois}}\n{{DuPage County, Illinois}}\n{{Chicago metropolitan area}}\n{{Chicago Landmarks}}\n{{Illinois}}\n{{Midwestern United States}}\n{{Pan American Games host cities}}\n{{Illinois cities and mayors of 100,000 population}}\n{{World's most populated urban areas}}\n}}\n{{Subject bar|portal1= Chicago|portal2= Illinois |portal3= United States|commons=yes|wikt=yes|n=yes|n-search=Category:Chicago|q=yes|s=yes|b=yes|voy=yes|v=yes|d=yes|d-search=Q1297}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Chicago| ]]\n[[Category:1833 establishments in Illinois]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Cities in Cook County, Illinois]]\n[[Category:Cities in DuPage County, Illinois]]\n[[Category:Cities in the Chicago metropolitan area]]\n[[Category:Cities in Illinois]]\n[[Category:County seats in Illinois]]\n[[Category:Inland port cities and towns of the United States]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1833]]\n[[Category:Populated places on Lake Michigan]]\n[[Category:Railway towns in Illinois]]\n", "text_old": "{{pp-vandalism|small=yes}}\n{{About|the city in Illinois}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{short description|City and county seat of Cook County, Illinois, United States}}\n{{Use American English|date = March 2019}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=August 2018}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name = Chicago, Illinois\n| settlement_type = [[List of cities in Illinois|City]]\n| official_name = City of Chicago\n| image_skyline = Chicago montage1.jpg\n| imagesize = 300px\n| image_caption                   = Clockwise from top: [[Chicago Loop|Downtown]], the [[Chicago Theatre]], the [[Chicago \"L\"|'L']], [[Navy Pie