 October 2012, the University of Kansas' athletic department had not accepted Missouri's invitations to play inter-conference rivalry games, putting the rivalry on hold. Sports clubs sponsored by the two universities continued to play each other.<ref name=\"Border Showdown Continues\">{{cite web|title=Border Showdown Continues|url=http://mizzoumag.missouri.edu/2012/07/border-showdown-continues/|accessdate=2012-10-23}}</ref>\n\n===Current===\n<!-- IF YOU UPDATE THIS TABLE, PLEASE UPDATE THE DATE AT THE BOTTOM -->\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Rivalry!!Name<br>(Trophy)!!Games Played!!Began\n|-\n| [[Baylor\u2013TCU football rivalry|Baylor\u2013TCU]] || The Revivalry || 115 || 1899\n|-\n| [[Baylor\u2013Texas Tech football rivalry|Baylor\u2013Texas Tech]] || Texas Farm Bureau Insurance Shootout || 77 || 1929\n|-\n| [[Iowa State\u2013Kansas State football rivalry|Iowa State\u2013Kansas State]] || Farmageddon || 102 || 1917\n|-\n| [[Kansas\u2013Kansas State football rivalry|Kansas\u2013Kansas State]] || Sunflower Showdown<br>(Governor's Cup) || 116 || 1902\n|-\n| [[Bedlam Series|Oklahoma\u2013Oklahoma State]] || Bedlam<br>(Bedlam Bell) || 113 || 1904\n|-\n| [[Red River Showdown|Oklahoma\u2013Texas]] || Red River Showdown<br>(Golden Hat) || 114 || 1900\n|-\n| [[TCU\u2013Texas Tech football rivalry|TCU\u2013Texas Tech]] || West Texas Championship<br>(Saddle Trophy) || 61 || 1926\n|-\n| [[Texas\u2013Texas Tech football rivalry|Texas\u2013Texas Tech]] || (Chancellor's Spurs) || 68 || 1928\n|-\n\n| colspan=\"4\"  style=\"font-size:8pt; text-align:center;\"|'''Reference:<ref>Records by School\n* \"Baylor\": {{Cite news|url=http://www.winsipedia.com/baylor|title=Winsipedia - Baylor Bears football all-time record, wins, and statistics|work=Winsipedia|access-date=2018-01-25|language=en}}\n* \"Iowa State\": {{Cite news|url=http://www.winsipedia.com/iowa-state|title=Winsipedia - Iowa State Cyclones football all-time record, wins, and statistics|work=Winsi